title: Tyreek backs Tua, OBJ options, AJ Brown claps back, Biggest expectations, and Russell Wilson Top 5?
itunes:title: Tyreek backs Tua, OBJ options, AJ Brown claps back, Biggest expectations, and Russell Wilson Top 5?
description:
The Good Morning Football Podcast begins with Tyreek Hill's glowing words about Tua Tagovailoa. Hosts Kyle Brandt, Will Selva, Tom Pelissero and Fmr NFL DB Darius Butler discuss why Hill's words were so important for the Dolphins upcoming season.  All four hosts have different opinions on where OBJ should play.  Tom explains why he thinks the AFC West has the biggest expectations this season.  Plus, Will shows how Russell Wilson is still a Top 5 quarterback in the NFL.

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
